splayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776149386453,"sessionId":"fe9e5cb9-8ab0-4743-90aa-26f70c5fc4b7","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":33806,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776143737903,"endedAt":1776143897307,"runtimeMs":21717,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/fe9e5cb9-8ab0-4743-90aa-26f70c5fc4b7.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions_send timed out again. The QLHV group session seems to be not responsive. The state file was saved successfully. Let me try a different approach - send to the master-orchestrator main session with the correct delivery context.\n\nActually, the cron job has `delivery.mode = \"announce\"` which means it sends to the channel where the cron fires. But this cron fires in the cron session (6f3323ef), not the QLHV group. The delivery to -5163901258 timed out.\n\nLet me try the main master-orchestrator session which shows the QLHV group as its last channel:\n\n\nLooking at the main orchestrator session, it's currently running and directed to telegram:direct:6053576134, not the QLHV group. The last QLHV group session ended around 06:32 and the current one is still running but unresponsive to session sends. I could try the DTLX group instead, but that's also ended. The cron job itself should be handling the delivery, so let me just report the state and let the system handle the routing.\n\nSince the cron delivery failed before, I'll update the heartbeat state and return the plain text summary as instructed. The external recipient needs to go to -5163901258, but the current cron session can't reach it through sessions_send. The parent session is also failing, so I'll just return the report text and let the cron job's delivery mode handle the actual sending."},{"type":"text","text":"🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 06:49 UTC 14 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• ⛔ subagent **8bffa95f** (DTLX Full API Test v2) — **FAILED** after ~6m runtime — timeout + providerSpecificData errors (both models failed)\n• ℹ️ Parent session telegram:direct:6053576134 still affected by 500 errors\n\nPipeline: **DEGRADED**\n• Active sessions: 5 (cron 5p ✅ cron Agent Status ✅ QLHV group ✅ main ✅ this cron ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Blockers: mongosh connectivity | JWT `doc.id` undefined bug | AHV-Holding-TroLy 500 errors\n\n*(Note: sessions_send to -5163901258 timed out — QLHV group session unresponsive to programmatic pings. State updated. Cron delivery mechanism should handle the push; if not, Lead should check the QLHV group session.)*\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":219,"output":521,"totalTokens":34327,"cacheRead":31367,"cacheWrite":2220,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776149549395,"responseId":"062d172f70ef1a9766906c71e9a44e5f","__openclaw":{"id":"ac54418e","seq":10}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"heartbeat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"heartbeat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776149296907,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":42081,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776149263572,"endedAt":1776149290619,"runtimeMs":27047,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see some important changes:\n1. Lead direct session (6053576134) is now `failed` status (ended at 06:46 UTC)\n2. There's a new subagent running