"feat(tuition): finance-style tuition management page redesign\n\n- Finance/fintech aesthetic with deep navy + clean whites + green/red accents\n- TuitionSummaryCards: 4-card grid (total receivable, collected, pending, overdue)\n- TuitionFilters: search + status + date range with clear-all\n- TuitionTable: sortable columns (name/paid/total/debt/date/status), paginated\n- Status badges: Đã đóng (emerald) / Đóng 1 phần (amber) / Quá hạn (rose)\n- TuitionDetailModal: student info + fee breakdown + progress bar + payment history\n- Export CSV button\n- Build + lint pass\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":160,"output":238,"totalTokens":37454,"cacheRead":36679,"cacheWrite":377,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776070156653,"responseId":"062be110adddb6aa67bc74fcaf33581e","__openclaw":{"id":"67dc38f7","seq":79}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5212380728","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776050780124,"sessionId":"cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":86945,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776042657727,"endedAt":1776042674188,"runtimeMs":16461,"childSessions":["agent:senior-backend:subagent:31b6b412-927a-481a-b157-d89c2dd3a187","agent:code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd-07f8-4a08-a4d6-823d773bfe5b","agent:security-reviewer:subagent:6739034d-567f-4c51-8557-f54f81ff565a","agent:database-reviewer:subagent:51a096dc-1f97-4452-938a-8b629dc4e57e","agent:performance-optimizer:subagent:57b179b5-c044-4440-ac46-e970badda4d1","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:fd28add5-35bd-45b1-8ac5-93bd476867bc"],"thinkingLevel":"medium","systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5212380728","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Another heartbeat with degraded status from cron session. But I'm already responding to Khương directly. This is just the cron session reporting - I don't need to do anything."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n*(Đã nhận — Khương đã có thông tin trực tiếp)*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":273,"output":70,"totalTokens":86706,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":86363,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776050343276,"responseId":"062b93a9d7d57450ade805668e7bbc2f","__openclaw":{"id":"034a9ad0","seq":399}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 03:23 UTC 13 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• 5p main cron (ed2d0b5d) **ENDED** — completed monitoring cycle\n• 6f3323ef DTLX cron still **running** ✅\n• DTLX group session (ba02d9fc) **ENDED** after settings page work\n• QLHV group session (b90d0cbf) now **running** since ~01:56 UTC ✅\n• ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (backend + frontend) — pre-existing baseline, no change\n\nPipeline: **DEGRADED**\n• Active sessions: 3\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: ⚠️ DTLX subagent crashes (persistent) — no new failures\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776050763149,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"3a62ef52","seq":400}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Another heartbeat. This one seems to be from the older cron session that's still sending alerts about pre-existing DTLX subagent failures. These are known historical failures from the AHV Works review session yesterday. No action needed."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n*(DTLX subagent failures = known baseline from yesterday's AHV Works review — GitLab LFS issue, đã xử lý)*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":286,"output":86,"totalTokens":87031,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":78881,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776050763254,"responseId":"062b954c56347f54993c06cd44a06cac","__openclaw":{"id":"651d500e","seq":401}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","label":"ahv-qlhv-fe:senior-frontend","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776045239808,"sessionId":"f11e16e1-b3ee-4f6a-9488-c7dc7ff1dba4","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":18902,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776045137783,"endedAt":1776045618483,"runtimeMs":378751,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/f11e16e1-b3ee-4f6a-9488-c7dc7ff1dba4.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both edits were successful. Now let me run lint to verify everything is correct."},{"type":"text","text":"Both fixes applied. Let me verify with lint:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_49i56tnx1gv5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe && yarn lint 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":180,"output":85,"totalTokens":18987,"cacheRead":13466,"cacheWrite":5256,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp