{"type":"message","id":"b4b2608a","parentId":"47573d12","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:54:54.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture:\n\n1. **DTLX BE is running** on port 3001 (PID 122018) — this is different from the MEMORY.md which said port 5555. Let me check which codebase this is.\n\nWait - there are TWO DTLX backends potentially:\n1. The old one in `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend` (which MEMORY.md says runs on port 5555)\n2. The new one in `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend` (which seems to be running on port 3001)\n\n\n3. The subagent session tested the new codebase on port 3001, but MEMORY.md still shows the old codebase running on port 5555 — I need to verify which one is actually active and what the current state is.\n\nLooking at the session results, the DTLX BE on port 3001 has auth endpoints working (signin passes), but there are critical blockers: JWT tokens are missing the user `id` field due to a mismatch between what `token.service.js` expects (`doc.id`) and what Mongoose lean docs actually return (`doc._id`), and protected endpoints fail with 401 errors. The `/auth/register` and `/auth/profile` endpoints don't exist in the codebase either. The subagent that was running tests has since ended, so I need to check the current server status and consolidate findings for the lead.","thinkingSignature":"628a50fea1c4ad715b7d984a8810ac75a9d199c9e2b0f1f09e34149c3c7a71e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_io7o8u8pvp0y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"}' | head -c 300; echo \"\"; curl -s http://localhost:5555/api/v1/auth/login -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"email\":\"admin2@gmail.com\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"}' 2>/dev/null | head -c 200; echo \"\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1942,"output":444,"cacheRead":20041,"cacheWrite":29476,"totalTokens":51903,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776149678066,"responseId":"062d17afe5b4719ec4bd5d3a4a4758a7"}}
