{"type":"message","id":"42364f00","parentId":"6f11149d","timestamp":"2026-04-15T03:12:04.349Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is asking me to create a Clean Architecture migration plan. I have all the data I need from my analysis. Let me now create a comprehensive plan and publish it to Confluence DTLX space as a proper document.\n\nLet me compile the full analysis:\n\n**Current State:**\n- 2/43 modules fully migrated (Clean Architecture): `teacherInfos`, `saleInfos`\n- `courses`, `coursesStudents`, `users` partially migrated (have entities/repos defined but services still use direct model)\n- 39 modules still fully legacy (direct Mongoose model access in services)\n\n**Clean Architecture Structure (already in place):**\n\n\nI've got the domain layer with entities and repository interfaces, the application layer with use cases and DTOs, and the infrastructure layer with implementations. The presentation layer already has clean architecture controllers with routes configured.\n\n**Modules Analysis (sorted by complexity/size):**\nLooking at the top legacy modules by service size to identify the migration priority—users is the largest at 2057 lines, followed by payments at 1079, studentInfos at 1050, lessons at 1043, coursesStudents at 836, exams at 704, courses at 585, and leadInfos at 498 lines.\n\nNow I'm organizing the remaining modules and grouping them by business domain to structure the migration phases systematically.","thinkingSignature":"b19fc3afd252186b362abdb82fe900fe8ce76e92f51c23ad8459403b733925b0"},{"type":"text","text":"Đã có đầy đủ data. Đang tạo kế hoạch chi tiết.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kidpgb9woe0x_1","name":"confluence-dtlx__confluence_search_pages","arguments":{"query":"OTLXPA1","spaceKey":"DTLX","limit":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":458,"output":356,"cacheRead":10789,"cacheWrite":54261,"totalTokens":65864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776222698294,"responseId":"062e34ebffa1e555995039e9542e4e5a"}}
